    </para>
   </step>
   <step>
    <para>
     Right-click the printer you want to delete and choose
     <guimenu>Delete</guimenu>. Confirm with <guimenu>OK</guimenu>.
    </para>
   </step>
   <step>
    <para>
     Type the root password and click <guimenu>Authenticate</guimenu>.
